This application must be entirely frontend with no server dependencies.

## Requirements

- No server-side code (no Express, Fastify, or any backend frameworks)
- No server dependencies in package.json
- Use static file serving only (Vite dev server for development)
- All functionality must run in the browser
- Build output should be static files that can be deployed to GitHub Pages
- No API calls to external servers unless absolutely necessary
- Use client-side routing if needed
- All data should be embedded or fetched from static files

## Allowed

- Vite dev server for development (npm run dev)
- Static file serving
- Client-side JavaScript/TypeScript
- CSS frameworks and styling
- Three.js and other frontend libraries
- Static data files (JSON, images, etc.)

## Not Allowed

- Express, Fastify, or any backend framework
- Server-side rendering (SSR)
- Database connections
- Server-side API endpoints
- Backend authentication
- Server-side file processing

## Deployment

- Build output should be static files in dist/ folder
- Ready for GitHub Pages deployment
- No server configuration needed